Package com.intellij.execution.configurations

Class CommandLineState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.execution.configurations.CommandLineState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RunProfileState
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JavaCommandLineState, PythonCommandLineState, RunAnythingRunProfileState, XsltCommandLineState

    public abstract class CommandLineState
extends java.lang.Object
implements RunProfileState
    Base implementation of RunProfileState. Takes care of putting together a process and a console and wrapping them into an ExecutionResult. Does not contain any logic for actually starting the process.
    See Also:
    JavaCommandLineState, GeneralCommandLine
